cc:Work.dc:title: Ghost in the Shell - Misc Vector Art
cc:Work.dc:description:
Based upon the Ghost in the Shell: SAC anime
* INTER GATE: the gates that features in some of the cyberspace scenes.
* Communication Window: The comunication window that is shown when characters are talking with each other via their cyberbrains. Similar windows are used for documents, emails etc... so it might make a good template for the other types of windows.
* Laughing Man Logo: The logo the puppet master uses to obsecure himself from public view (modified version of one by euxneks), this version has a slightly diffrent text and should be eaiser to animate by rotating the text.
